Package common.connector.messages

package common.connector.messages
Messages related to the IConnector system.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    IAddPeersMsg
    Add a set of INamedConnectors to a ChatApp instance's set of peers.
    IConnectorErrMsg
    A message representing an error that occurred while processing another message at the IConnector level.
    IConnectorFailMsg
    A message representing a failure that occurred while processing another message at the IConnector level.
    IConnectorMsg
    A type-narrowed IDataPacketData, denoting a message that can be sent to an IConnector.
    IConnectorRejectMsg
    A message indicating that an earlier message was rejected during processing at the IConnector level.
    IConnectorStatusMsg
    A message representing a status that occurred while processing another message at the IConnector level.
    IInviteMsg
    Invite a ChatApp instance to a chat room, represented by its UUID and friendly name.
    IQuitMsg
    Remove the sender from the receiving ChatApp's set of peers.
    ISyncPeersMsg
    Synchronize the peers of two fully-connected networks of ChatApps.
